description: BE Group AB engages in trading and servicing of steel and aluminum products. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane and currently employs 609 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2006-11-24. The company offers the distribution and pre-processing of steel and aluminum to industrial companies, primarily building constructors and engineering companies. The firm operates in such countries as Sweden, Finland, Poland, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania. Its product range comprises commercial steel, engineering steel, stainless steel and aluminum. The company offers also such services as cutting and sawing, surface finishing, prefabricated reinforcing, logistics, advisory and warehousing, among others. The firm is a parent entity of a capital group, which, as of December 31, 2011, consisted of 13 subsidiaries.
